reviewText: You have to be careful when buying movies packaged together like this. If each movie isn't on it's own individual disc the quality almost always suffers. This collection is properly made and enjoyable to watch because all four movies are each on their own individual disc. While that in and of itself won't guarantee quality, it's a good indication that quality was considered when the collection was decided upon to make.
summary: Multi Feature Collection, Easy Money, et al
